#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyboard Usage"
msgstr "Korištenje tastature"

#. Tag: para
#: keyboard-commands.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this chapter you will learn how to use the keyboard effectively, because "
"most operations can be done more quickly by keyboard than with the mouse. It "
"will take some time to learn the <link linkend=\"key_bindings\">Key-"
"Bindings</link>, but mastering them saves you a lot of time. Please note "
"that &krusader; can use <link linkend=\"configure-shortcuts\">Key-binding "
"Profiles</link> to swap easily to other Key-binding setups, &eg; of other "
"commanders, or you can create your own key-bindings."
msgstr ""
"U ovom poglavlju ćete naučiti kako da efikasno koristite tastaturu, jer "
"većina operacija se može učiniti mnogo brže preko tastature nego pomoću "
"miša. To će potrajati neko vrijeme, da se nauči <link linkend=\"key_bindings"
"\">Povezivanja tipki</link>, ali u biti štedi vam puno vremena. Imajte na "
"umu da &krusader; može koristiti <link linkend=\"configure-shortcuts\">Key-"
"povezniece Profil</link> da lako prevasi na podešavanja druge Key-"
"poveznicama &eg; drugih komandi, ili možete kreirati vlastito značenje "
"tastera."

#. Tag: para
#: keyboard-commands.docbook:23
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "After <link linkend=\"starting-krusader\"> starting</link> &krusader;, "
#| "the keyboard action can begin. Use <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
#| "<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> to jump to the <link linkend=\"list_panel"
#| "\">Location Toolbar</link> where you can type the desired directory. "
#| "After <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Down arrow</keycap></"
#| "keycombo> you are in the <link linkend=\"termemu\">Terminal emulator</"
#| "link> and you can type any command you desire. Use <keycombo action="
#| "\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Up arrow</keycap></keycombo> to jump back to the "
#| "active panel. If you want to jump to a file or directory that starts with "
#| "<literal>f</literal>, then simply press <keycap>f</keycap> on the "
#| "keyboard to use the <link linkend=\"quicksearch\">Quick search</link>. "
#| "Use the &Enter; key to execute the file or to open a directory that has "
#| "the focus. Be sure to remember the Function Keys - <keycap>F3</keycap> to "
#| "View, <keycap>F4</keycap> to Edit, <keycap>F5</keycap> to Copy, <keycombo "
#| "action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>U</keycap></keycombo> to Unpack, "
#| "&etc;"
msgid ""
"After starting &krusader;, the keyboard action can begin. Use <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> to jump to the <link "
"linkend=\"list_panel\">Location Toolbar</link> where you can type the "
"desired folder. After <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Down;</keycombo> you "
"are in the <link linkend=\"termemu\">Terminal emulator</link> and you can "
"type any command you desire, provided that the <link linkend=\"konfig-startup"
"\">terminal is shown</link>. Use <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Up;</"
"keycombo> to jump back to the active panel. If you want to jump to a file or "
"folder that starts with <literal>f</literal>, then simply press <keycap>f</"
"keycap> on the keyboard to use the <link linkend=\"quicksearch\">search bar</"
"link>. Use the &Enter; key to execute the file or to open a folder that has "
"the focus. Be sure to remember the Function Keys - <keycap>F3</keycap> to "
"View, <keycap>F4</keycap> to Edit, <keycap>F5</keycap> to Copy, <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>U</keycap></keycombo> to Unpack, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Nakon <link linkend=\"starting-krusader\"> pokretanja</link> &krusader;, "
"akcije tastature mogu početi. Koristite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> za skočiti na <link linkend=\"list_panel"
"\">Lokacijski Toolbar</link> gdje možete upisati željeni direktorij. Nakon "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>dolje sterlica </keycap></keycombo> "
"ste u <link linkend=\"termemu\">Terminal Emulatoru</link> i možete upisati "
"bilo koju komandu želite. Koristite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>Strelica gore</keycap></keycombo> za skočiti natrag u aktivni panel. "
"Ako želite da skoči u datoteku ili direktorij koji počinje s <literal>f</"
"literal>,jednostavno pritisnite <keycap>f</keycap> na tastaturi da koristite "
"<link linkend=\"quicksearch\">Brzu pretraga</link>. Koristite &Enter; tipku "
"za izvršiti datoteku ili za otvaranje direktorija koji ima fokus. Budite "
"sigurni da ste zapamtili  funkcijske tipke - <keycap>F3</keycap> za pregled, "
"<keycap>F4</keycap> za uređivanje, <keycap>F5</keycap> kopirati, <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>The</keycap></keycombo> raspakirajte "
"ga, &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: keyboard-commands.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also perform several operations with the <link linkend=\"folder-tabs"
"\">Folder tabs</link>, including several <link linkend=\"edit-menu"
"\">selection</link> operations. And at the end you can close &krusader; with "
"<keycap>F10</keycap>."
msgstr ""
"Također možete obavljati više operacija sa <link linkend=\"folder-tabs"
"\">Folder tabovima</link>, uključujući i nekoliko <link linkend=\"edit-menu"
"\">Izbor</link> operacija. I na kraju možete zatvoriti &krusader; sa "
"<keycap>F10</keycap>."

